{
  "stem": "11174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was very strict with me, and I didn't have a lot of fun, no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To him there was one thing-- if you learn, keep on learning then you'll write.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If you're not, no matter what you do is nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he was very strict to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wasn't soft on any-- in any way or shape or form.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother was soft.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She always tried to, to soften up things, but he was very, very strict.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And now I'm thankful to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I realize how right he was because I-- I'm a father, a grandfather myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But as a teenager it was very, very tough, very miserable almost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he only knew one thing-- you got to sit and learn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And if you just took off for a little while, you were already on the dog's list, [LAUGHS] so to speak.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But generally was a nice, warm life in the house and then the children all loved each other and we were a very happy family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure ?], my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A matter of fact, my grandfather that you see here [POINTS], the picture, he was still alive when all his children, grandchildren except me-- I was was already-- killed out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he, the Germans killed him in a-- in a ghetto in Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- he lived in another town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was rabbi before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before my father, he was rabbi, so it was his father, his grandfather rabbi in that same little town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then he moved away to another town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The name was Brigel in Yiddish or Brzesko in Polish, Brzesko Slotwina it was called.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's right near Tarnow-- between Tarnow and Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
